{"tid":279299,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[星島港聞] 鄭松泰：大眾白癡才與梁游扮friend以為我哋係本土派","createTime":"2017-06-11T07:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T07:43:13.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"27b327c2250c5ef506c5ac788b1d47c4ae22f90e","tid":279299,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T07:28:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.stheadline.com/inews-content.php?cat=a&amp;nid=112417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finews-content.php%3Fcat%3Da%26nid%3D112417&d=ejsX3kHsxERRDkFiosH%2B%2BJUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=cf13561f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finews-content.php%3Fcat%3Da%26nid%3D112417&h=ccc63dd3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.stheadline.com/inews-content.php?cat=a&amp;nid=112417</a><br />\n<br />\n   前城大校董仇思達昨晚在網台播出一段聲稱是熱血公民立法會議員鄭松泰的錄音，當中提到要與青年新政梁頌恆、游蕙禎「扮friend」，是因為「大眾白癡」。鄭松泰其後在facebook回應，指熱血公民工作組的內部溝通外洩，對於有手足沒有遵守黨規深感遺憾，他其後再補充指，支持梁游而令黃毓民敗選是智力有問題。<br />\n      <br />\n      仇思達昨晚在節目中播出一條聲稱是鄭松泰的錄音聲帶，聲帶中未有透露發生的時間及場合，有一把疑似鄭松泰的男聲說話，當中提到：「我喺公眾場合，我要同佢哋扮friend，我要係我立場上顯示俾其他人知道我係幫緊佢哋，因為大眾白癡吖嘛，佢哋以為我地係本土派呀！以為本土派係同一批人嚟，有人以為我係青年新政，你明唔明呀，喺加拿大，係咁樣嘛。」<br />\n      <br />\n      鄭松泰沒有否認錄音，並在facebook回應：自己在熱血公民工作組所發表的工作匯報和內部溝通被人流出，對於有手足沒有遵守黨規和破壞內部溝通指引，深表遺憾」。他又指，該內部限時直播的講話，沒有什麼是不可對人言，亦沒有什麼是秘密或所謂大揭秘。至於內容溝通為何會出現如此狀況，他們會好好檢討及改善。<br />\n      <br />\n      他再補充指：「9月4日當日有份支持梁游而令教主黃毓民敗選的人，全部都是智力有問題。而今日我們則要共同面對這個共業。」"},{"pid":"a6477d1e3c410e74a29e995c4a538d9c5643afa3","tid":279299,"uid":33605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T07:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鄭松泰收皮"},{"pid":"902bab1ee34d19715bf5e4c4e6a43fc81d116044","tid":279299,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T07:31:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為本土派係同一批人嚟，有人以為我係青年新政，你明唔明呀，喺<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">加拿大</span></span>，係咁樣嘛。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">投熱血班人係港豬<br />\n<br />\n加拿大嗰班尤其豬！</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d25166ee39eb78d6c8f5de26e1c98493060c4d","tid":279299,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T07:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/7/2017/06/11/8/819f5b6553eb018fe134bcbc64c94512.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F7%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F8%2F819f5b6553eb018fe134bcbc64c94512.jpg&h=cc2e9347&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f1f49a08b01339db3a108d31d427e745a7cd4b1","tid":279299,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T07:37:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今晚9:30PM<br />\n仇思達又開波啦！</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chaust\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchaust&d=ejsX3kHsxERRDkFiosH%2B%2BJUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=332d50b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chaust</a>"},{"pid":"8806e6063de5e5a41c5b2323bcf6e8b548d556a8","tid":279299,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T07:37:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1cjewO6zf1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1cjewO6zf1s&d=ejsX3kHsxERRDkFiosH%2B%2BJUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=ae40c19f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1cjewO6zf1s</a><br />\n11:36<br />\n甄生一早知鄭松泰係咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57ef4460e03c89d47da27810107fdd0d708c959","tid":279299,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T07:39:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-